_:N0fe46fc2aa6748618013fbe407abd995 <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Dormant Assets Commission was tasked with identifying new pools of dormant assets and working with industry to encourage the contribution of these assets to good causes. The Commission <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/2-billion-boost-set-to-transform-charity-and-voluntary-sector-funding\">published its report on 3 March 2017</a>. Please click <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dormant-assets-commission-final-report-to-government\">here</a> for a copy of the report.</p>\n\n<p>Should you have questions, please contact <a href=\"mailto:dormant-assets@culture.gov.uk\">dormant-assets@culture.gov.uk</a>.</p>\n\n</div>" .
_:N0fe46fc2aa6748618013fbe407abd995 <http://schema.org/text> "The independent Dormant Assets Commission was formed in March 2016. The work of the Commission has now ended. " .
